---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { SITE } from '../config/site';
---

<Base title="Privacy policy" description="What data this site collects, and what it doesn't.">
  <section class="wrap prose">
    <h1 class="page-title">Privacy policy</h1>
    <p class="small muted">Last updated: July 2026</p>

    <p>
      {SITE.name} ({SITE.domain}) is a static website. We keep data collection to the minimum
      needed to run the site.
    </p>

    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Nothing you type.</strong> This site has no accounts, no comments, and no
        forms. We never ask for or store your personal information through the site.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Basic, anonymous traffic data.</strong> Our hosting provider (Cloudflare)
        processes standard server logs, such as IP address and browser type, to serve the
        site and protect it from abuse.
        <!-- 如果以后加了分析工具(如 Cloudflare Web Analytics / Plausible),在这里补一条说明。 -->
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
    <p>
      Some outbound links are affiliate links. When you click one, the destination site may
      set its own cookies to attribute the referral. Those cookies belong to the provider's
      site and are governed by their privacy policy, not ours. See our
      <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/">affiliate disclosure</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Email</h2>
    <p>
      If you email us at <a href={`mailto:${SITE.contactEmail}`}>{SITE.contactEmail}</a>,
      we use your address only to reply. We do not add you to any list or share your
      address with anyone.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>Any change to this policy will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-title { padding-top: 2rem; }
</style>
